original: Yours for just $1,000,000!  Don't pass up this unbelievable opportunity to live out your dotcom dream.  FM is dead!  Podcasting is the future of radio! Online radio is the future of radio.  Any idiot with a computer can become a DJ these days and play other people's works while objecting to royalty fees.  Where there are idiots, there is money.  This domain name will make you rich.  Buy it today.
translated: 只要$1,000,000！不要错过这个千载难逢的机会，实现你的网络创业之梦。广播电台已死！播客才是电台的未来！网络电台才是电台的未来。只要有台电脑，哪个傻逼都能成为DJ，播别人的作品还不用交版权费。凡是存在白痴的地方，就存在商机。这个域名能让你发财。立刻购买吧。
